   219	        on_canonical_present: "Leave canonical review/ state untouched and do not overwrite it with legacy scratch artifacts."
   220	        on_legacy_detected: "Move only the review-specific whitelist, append a migration event to the canonical JSONL, and leave unrelated scratch files untouched."
   221	        on_conflict: "If canonical review/ state and legacy scratch review state both exist but disagree, halt for operator repair instead of merging contradictory state."
