## Focus
YAML workflow steps: fan-out spawn, artifact-root override branch, and lineage recursion guard.

## Findings
P1, .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-review-loop_auto.yaml:135, `step_fanout_spawn` only skips when `config.fanout` is absent, so a spawned lineage that still has `config.fanout` can recursively fan out instead of running only its own lineage. Fix: extend the guard to skip when `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` is present.

P1, .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-review-loop_confirm.yaml:135, Same missing lineage recursion guard in the confirm review workflow: the fan-out step is guarded only by `config.fanout is absent`. Fix: extend the guard to skip when `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` is present.

P1, .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-research-loop_auto.yaml:146, Same missing lineage recursion guard in the auto research workflow: the fan-out step is guarded only by `config.fanout is absent`. Fix: extend the guard to skip when `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` is present.

P1, .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-research-loop_confirm.yaml:130, Same missing lineage recursion guard in the confirm research workflow: the fan-out step is guarded only by `config.fanout is absent`. Fix: extend the guard to skip when `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` is present.

## Verdict
The artifact-root override branch is consistent across all four YAMLs, but the recursion guard is missing everywhere.
Review verdict: CONDITIONAL
